{"article_id":"pz0UvDJNow2iFIpe","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"President Donald Trump is currently deciding whether or not to release a controversial secret memo ,","depth":5},{"id":1,"text":"compiled by Rep. Devin Nunes","depth":6},{"id":2,"text":"( R-CA ) ,","depth":6},{"id":3,"text":"that alleges an anti-Trump conspiracy at the FBI .","depth":4},{"id":4,"text":"Republicans on the House Intelligence Committee voted on Monday night to release it ,","depth":5},{"id":5,"text":"though Democrats unanimously opposed it .","depth":5},{"id":6,"text":"The vote gave Trump five days","depth":5},{"id":7,"text":"to review the document","depth":6},{"id":8,"text":"and decide on its release .","depth":6},{"id":9,"text":"The president has previously indicated","depth":5},{"id":10,"text":"he wanted the memo made public ,","depth":5},{"id":11,"text":"and it could be released as early as Thursday .","depth":4},{"id":12,"text":"Now the FBI itself has weighed in against releasing the memo .","depth":5},{"id":13,"text":"On Wednesday , the FBI released a strongly worded statement","depth":7},{"id":14,"text":"expressing \" grave concerns \" about the memo ' s accuracy :","depth":7},{"id":15,"text":"The FBI takes seriously its obligations to the FISA Court and its compliance with procedures","depth":8},{"id":16,"text":"overseen by career professionals in the Department of Justice and the FBI .","depth":8},{"id":17,"text":"We are committed to working with the appropriate oversight entities","depth":8},{"id":18,"text":"to ensure the continuing integrity of the FISA process .","depth":8},{"id":19,"text":"With regard to the House Intelligence Committee ' s memorandum ,","depth":7},{"id":20,"text":"the FBI was provided a limited opportunity","depth":9},{"id":21,"text":"to review this memo the day","depth":10},{"id":22,"text":"before the committee voted to release it .","depth":10},{"id":23,"text":"As expressed during our initial review ,","depth":9},{"id":24,"text":"we have grave concerns about material omissions of fact","depth":10},{"id":25,"text":"that fundamentally impact the memo ' s accuracy .","depth":10},{"id":26,"text":"Rep. Adam Schiff","depth":11},{"id":27,"text":"( D-CA ) ,","depth":11},{"id":28,"text":"the top Democrat on the intelligence committee , said","depth":10},{"id":29,"text":"that he sided with the FBI .","depth":9},{"id":30,"text":"\" I think","depth":10},{"id":31,"text":"the FBI is exactly right .","depth":10},{"id":32,"text":"I have the same grave concerns over it. \"","depth":9},{"id":33,"text":"He added","depth":8},{"id":34,"text":"that he knew of the FBI ' s concerns","depth":9},{"id":35,"text":"before he voted against the memo ' s release .","depth":9},{"id":36,"text":"After his State of the Union address on Tuesday night , Trump told Rep. Jeff Duncan","depth":9},{"id":37,"text":"( R-SC )","depth":9},{"id":38,"text":"he would \" 100 percent \" make the memo public in the coming days .","depth":8},{"id":39,"text":"And on Wednesday , Chief of Staff John Kelly told Fox News Radio","depth":8},{"id":40,"text":"that the memo \" will be released here pretty quick ,","depth":9},{"id":41,"text":"I think ,","depth":10},{"id":42,"text":"and the whole world can see it . \"","depth":10},{"id":43,"text":"As my colleague Zack Beauchamp reported ,","depth":8},{"id":44,"text":"releasing the Nunes memo could lead to an open war between Trump and the FBI .","depth":8},{"id":45,"text":"But","depth":8},{"id":46,"text":"based on the FBI ' s latest statement ,","depth":9},{"id":47,"text":"it ' s possible the war has already begun .","depth":9},{"id":48,"text":"Update :","depth":2},{"id":49,"text":"This post has been updated with the possible release date of the Nunes memo .","depth":2}],"relations":[{"parent":99,"left":97,"right":98,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":97,"left":58,"right":96,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":58,"left":53,"right":57,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":53,"left":52,"right":3,"re